en_415357_0	A simple ceremony to donate 6 laptops to students at Sri Narada Vidyalaya and Ven Madihe Pannaseeha Vidyalaya in Putur got underway separately at both schools in Jaffna on Thursday (5).
en_415357_1	The 'Dhamma Deepa' Foundation at Sri Narada Buddhist Center - Colombo 07 sponsored the supply of those laptops to these schools for the benefit of children learning there.
en_415357_2	Both ceremonies, organized by the Security Force Headquarters - Jaffna (SFHQ-J) under the guidelines given by Major General Ruwan Wanigasooriya, Commander, Security Forces - Jaffna were attended by Buddhist monks, members of the donor foundation, 521 and 553 Brigade Commanders, school Principals, teachers, parents and students.
